 8→/**
 9→ * Performs the fold-left (forward accumulation) algorithm using the given IAccumulator
10→ * The general forward accumulation algorithm would not take an accumulator as a top-level
11→ * input parameter, instead the accumulator would be hidden inside the algorithm.   
12→ * But since the fold process, makes the folding process invariant and the accumulator the
13→ * variant piece, the accumulator is thus necessarily an input parameter here.
14→ * @author swong
15→ *
16→ */
17→public class FoldLAlgo implements IListAlgo {
18→
