 8→ * public class MyExtVisitorHost extends AExtVisitorHost&lt;MyIndex, MyExtVisitorHost&gt; {...}
 9→ * </pre>
10→ * @param <I>  The type of the index value that is being used.
11→ * @param <H>  The type of the concrete SUBCLASS that extends this class.
